README apksigcopier


REQUIREMENTS
============

* (optional) apksigner from android-sdk-build-tools-bin package
Required to compare two APKs by copying the signature from the first to a copy
of the second and checking if the resulting APK verifies.

Install android-sdk-build-tools-bin package and add
/opt/android-sdk/build-tools/ to the PATH.


